Description: evaluation runner for clnkr-compatible agents
 clankerval is the standalone evaluation runner extracted from clnkr.
 It runs project-owned evaluation suites, ships the canonical clankerval
 command, and provides clnkeval as a compatibility alias during the
 rename. The package also installs a tiny dummy suite and fixture agent
 under /usr/share/doc/clankerval/examples for smoke tests and examples.
